data.title: Comparative Law
data.meta_description: In Custody - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or view presentation slides online. This document provides an inmate custody report from the Stanislaus County Sheriff's Department listing 120 inmates currently in custody. It includes each inmate's name, booking number, date of birth, place of birth, arresting agency, time of arrest, current facility, booking date and potential release date. For each inmate it also lists the charges against them including the penal code violation, case number and bail amount if applicable. The report shows basic identifying and custody information for a large number of currently incarcerated individuals.
